title: I'm levl 30, but can't post...
body: I'm lvl 30 but I can not reply to posts?

replies.body: Sometimes an account may need to sync with the  boards, and a post can do just that.   It can also be a caching issue, where you are 30 but not may see it on your side.  Clearing your [cache](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or running on Incognito should show the real you.  You look to be showing as 30 now!
It also was not submitted 6 hours ago..
